Author: oharacopter
Text: i hate feeling how im mass if that makes sense, like i wish i could just be totally weightless and not take up any space. not just because of my ed but also because it just feels weird and wrong.

Author: fishonthesun
Text: I think I relate to some of this. I have PTSD and dissociate quite often. It almost feels like I'm watching someone else play a POV game of my life.  Also, when I look in the mirror, I just cant seem to comprehend what I see. Like I can study my face and say "this half of my face looks different to that half" and brutally tear my appearance of my body apart, but it's like I can only view one aspect separately, and that I cant put them all together to know what I look like as a person.  I constantly get a feeling that I wasnt meant to be a human.
